_:N23ced6d3bcc4409ba7ea388210dcb027 <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><h2 id=\"home-office-press-office\">Home Office press office</h2>\n\n<p>Journalists with enquiries can call the Home Office news desk on 0300 123 3535.</p>\n\n<p>The desk operates from 7am to 7pm, Monday to Friday.</p>\n\n<div class=\"call-to-action\">\n  <p>The Home Office press office is unable to answer calls from members of the public. If you are not a member of the media, <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/contact-the-home-office\">find the right part of the Home Office to contact</a>.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h3 id=\"out-of-hours\">Out of hours</h3>\n\n<p>Press office out of hours number: 07623 514 628. Only urgent media calls will be attended to.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"textphone-users\">Textphone users</h3>\n\n<p>Textphone: 07860 023 039. Start your message with 514 628, followed by a space and then your message up to 120 characters.</p>\n\n<div class=\"call-to-action\">\n  <p>Abuse of Home Office staff will not be tolerated. We reserve the right not to engage with anyone who acts in an abusive manner.</p>\n</div>\n</div>" .
